subject: Basketball (College)
lead_paragraph: Domantas Sabonis had 14 points and 8 rebounds to help No. 10 Gonzaga defeat St. John’s, 73-66, on Friday night in the NIT Season Tip-Off championship game at Madison Square Garden.
